%div.row.span5
  %div.span5 
    = link_to request_bd_path(@id), {:title => @ti} do 
      %h2.blacklight-title_display 
        %i.icon-circle-arrow-right &nbsp;Borrow Direct
    Request your item from our Borrow Direct partners.
    Available in about 4 working days.

  %div.span5 
    = link_to request_recall_path(@id), {:title => @ti} do 
      %h2.blacklight-title_display 
        %i.icon-circle-arrow-right &nbsp;Recall
    Recall your item from another patron.
    Available in 9 to 14 working days

  %div.span5 
    = link_to request_ill_path(@id), {:title => @ti} do 
      %h2.blacklight-title_display 
        %i.icon-circle-arrow-right &nbsp;Interlibrary Loan
    Description of interlibrary loan.

  %div.span5 
    = link_to request_hold_path(@id), {:title => @ti} do 
      %h2.blacklight-title_display 
        %i.icon-circle-arrow-right &nbsp;Hold
    Wait for the current borrower to return your item.
    May take up to one year to become available.

